{"tid":1815461,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"健忘的香港人,你們還記得這些畫面嗎?","createTime":"2020-01-07T13:46:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T00:05:25.000Z","uid":310684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d8cb3177135760875d25b543c3949e6227433327","tid":1815461,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:46:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lcei9Lz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLcei9Lz.png&h=faee0b96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xU5Vsxh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxU5Vsxh.png&h=ac3a27fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2019年自由之夏,我地高呼著&quot;不分和勇&quot;, &quot;和勇一家親&quot;. 全因為依份團結同信任,令我地嘅屋企─ 香港,不被極權政府壓倒.<br />\n<br />\n時代革命延續至今, 因為遊行期間發生過種種&quot;捉鬼&quot;事件, 令勇武手足感到心灰意冷.直到今日(7/1),喺連登有幾隊&quot;勇武小隊&quot;一一宣稱要退出戰場,引起一場&quot;捉鬼風波&quot;.有人話係五毛挑撥離間,亦有人話係當前革命嘅步伐正重蹈&quot;雨傘革命&quot;嘅覆轍.<br />\n<br />\n今日(7/1)嘅&quot;捉鬼風波&quot;確實有損己方士氣,又令敵方得逞.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ONDG7Gs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FONDG7Gs.png&h=a67083c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NVO73eQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNVO73eQ.jpg&h=39e98693&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有見及此,我地應當一致尋求解決方法,而非以&quot;xxxx小隊退出抗爭&quot;為名去派膠.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">解決方法</span></span>如下(取至巴打: daytona):<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;1. 無視連登三毛<br />\n2. 制定簡單原則：如果再喺現場見到有人玩膠，即時屌到佢收皮，然後繼續做正經嘢.&quot; </span></span><br />\n(取至好文: 記唔記得太子站靈堂蛋糕事件？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1814900\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1814900</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區)<br />\n<br />\n我地目前處理&quot;捉鬼事件&quot;確實不完美,但絕對可改善. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">&quot;不捉鬼&quot;必須要成為革命嘅重大原則</span></span>,以確保和勇之間嘅信任度高,穩定軍心,<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全體一致將予頭直指中国共剷黨</span></span>.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;捉鬼&quot;會招至咩下場,相信都家傳戶曉,喺到唔再重複. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2014嘅&quot;雨傘革命&quot;</span><span style=\"color: red;\">就係義士用血換返黎嘅教訓</span></span>.所謂<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">前車可鑑</span></span>,我地實在要汲取教訓,然後再加以改善,進化.<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLC1opz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLC1opz.png&h=f356e525&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5jxAsQ9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5jxAsQ9.png&h=e4af38ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r4U7iXS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr4U7iXS.png&h=7eba07e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理非同勇武係香港嘅命運共同體, 既然本來就屬為一體,就應該互相信賴</span></span>,拒絕質疑對方.<br />\n<br />\n最後,小弟建議<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">遊行</span></span>期間,<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全體高呼&quot;不捉鬼&quot;嘅</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">口號</span></span>,以喚起大眾&quot;不捉鬼&quot;嘅意識.<br />\n若手足諗到相關口號,請留言,以集思廣益.<br />\n小弟先獻醜: &quot;<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和勇共同體,唔好再捉鬼</span></span>&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">小弟亦謹代表全體和理非向勇武致敬.</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u4rJBOF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu4rJBOF.jpg&h=74b26068&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港,時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"500bde4f3e79bb11b649512f0f8918678920cf6a","tid":1815461,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:47:59.000Z","msg":"小弟一介怯懦和理非,感激勇武無同我地割席.我亦<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">絕不跟勇武割席,係核彈都唔割.</span></span>"},{"pid":"4ae5c79904122a7f70b5d55a1f36f7f017329746","tid":1815461,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:48:29.000Z","msg":"和勇一家親"},{"pid":"9e9bf6ecb1b9a2263c3d3c29403f2c533098093c","tid":1815461,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:48:42.000Z","msg":"不完美,可改善"},{"pid":"a20f00ea4c220f376fe367073b557bc30d4ccfb4","tid":1815461,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:49:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">和勇共同體,唔好再捉鬼</span></span>"},{"pid":"5a84b76a9ec96dbb7eb7d99c22dc1f0a78b35dc4","tid":1815461,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:50:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">勿捉鬼</span></span>"},{"pid":"4888db88200e96ca88b0fda700fae12528842b5a","tid":1815461,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:51:54.000Z","msg":"若認同上文,請幫忙like and push. <br />\nP牌仔push唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14eff0a007f1180a2b83c47dbd53065a6f01836d","tid":1815461,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:53:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">和勇共同體,唔好再捉鬼</span></span>"},{"pid":"84a4aecf625ea1c06db7dcfae60b1f28a049500c","tid":1815461,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:53:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">和勇共同體,唔好再捉鬼</span></span>"},{"pid":"dfe7955137aae3fce91cb7a6578cea80ba17bcb3","tid":1815461,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc